{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_51_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "『誕生日にやりたいこと』、なんて書こうかな？\nなんでも叶えてくれるんだっけ",
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11100,
          "startTime": 17.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣さんの時も瑠依ちゃんの時も楽しそうだったなぁ\n……そうだ！",
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3250.271097999999,
          "startTime": 18.750271098
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん……何、書いてるの？　あ、それ……\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の……",
      "startTime": 24.7169377646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "事前アンケートだよ\nアイドル雑誌の有名企画、次は私の番なんだ",
      "startTime": 29.4333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "おめでとう……！　このお仕事、楽しんでほしい……\nすみれちゃんの、やりたいことって……？",
      "startTime": 38.7501575789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "こころが当ててみせましょう～\nずばり、トリエルのセンター強奪！　ですよね？",
      "startTime": 44.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ご、強奪！？　そんなことしないよー！\n無理矢理センターになっても嬉しくないし！",
      "startTime": 53.2751242955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、私が書いたのは……\n『みんなとおしるこを作って食べたい』だよ！",
      "startTime": 60.0084576289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "スーパーで材料を買って来て\nみんなでおしるこを作るの！",
      "startTime": 65.4417924881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そんなの今ここで出来るじゃないですか\nせっかくだし、もっと大きなことしましょうよ",
      "startTime": 71.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "例えば……すみれちゃんがおしるこを\nプロデュースするとか……そういうの……",
      "startTime": 79.7122904622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん。いろいろ考えたんだけどね\n前からやりたかったことをやるのもいいなーって",
      "startTime": 87.8535601933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "昔、学校の授業で農業体験した時に、自分で\nお米を作ったんだ。それがすっごく美味しくて",
      "startTime": 96.2535601933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "いつか、私が育てたもち米を使って、みんなで\nおしるこを作って食べたいと思ってたんだ",
      "startTime": 104.7868935267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今から田植えすると時間も手間もかかるし\nさすがに誕生日企画でも難しい気がして",
      "startTime": 113.1535601933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですかー？　こころなら、予算がなんぼのもん\nじゃーいって東京都サイズの田んぼをお願いしますけど",
      "startTime": 121.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……スタッフさんを困らせちゃダメだよ",
      "startTime": 125.4706107939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、自作のもち米じゃなくても、みんなで\nおしるこを作るだけで凄く楽しそうだし！",
      "startTime": 133.7807034809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……みんなでって、誰か誘ってたり……する？",
      "startTime": 137.3351687597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "まだ全然決めてないよ\n瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんは撮影日、別のお仕事だし……",
      "startTime": 145.7807034809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "私……すみれちゃんの誕生日企画、参加したい\n一緒に、とびきり美味しいおしるこ……作る！",
      "startTime": 154.7997049179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！　いいの？\nでも、雫ちゃん忙しいんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 160.7806983947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫。私のことは、気にせず……\nこころちゃんも、一緒にお手伝い……しよ",
      "startTime": 166.3427217968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇー。こころはちょ～っとこれから仕事が\nばちばちに忙しくなる予定で……",
      "startTime": 174.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "お願い、します……こころちゃんがいれば百人力……！\n凄く楽しくなると思う……絶対、絶対、絶対……！",
      "startTime": 181.2514887659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、雫ちゃん……ち、近い近い！\nぐいぐい来過ぎですっ！",
      "startTime": 189.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……しょうがないですねー。美味しいおしるこ\nが食べられるなら、私も手伝ってあげるとしましょう",
      "startTime": 196.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13551.012420500001,
          "startTime": 210.3176790872
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、こころちゃん、ありがとう！\nふふ、企画の日が楽しみだなー！",
      "startTime": 206.1843476612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "……こころちゃん、ちょっと\nこの後……時間、ある？",
      "startTime": 215.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "なんでしょうか？　売れっ子のこころは一分一秒も\n無駄に出来ませんが、少しだけなら構いませんよ",
      "startTime": 221.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "ん……ありがと\nすみれちゃんの誕生日企画についてなんだけど――",
      "startTime": 228.1023733626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――誕生日企画撮影、当日",
      "startTime": 233.1690400293,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1818.4805381000047,
          "startTime": 234.9875205674
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4185.147204700002,
          "startTime": 237.354187234
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 234.535702627
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 234.535702627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "山形の実家の近くで撮影するって聞いたんだけど……\nあれ、うちはこっちじゃないよ？",
      "startTime": 242.0208537736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 245.4722198976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_51_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫。合ってる……ん、着いた\nじゃじゃーん……ここで、撮影する",
      "startTime": 249.8388794432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 253.6722198976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
